### Invalid request

POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Register

POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Love",
    "lastName": "Rembo",
    "email": "rembo1234@gmail.com",
    "phone": "+254734567890",
    "password": "rembo@1234"
}

